com.biasedbit.efflux.session

Class MultiParticipantSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.biasedbit.efflux.session.AbstractRtpSession
      • com.biasedbit.efflux.session.MultiParticipantSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControlPacketReceiver, DataPacketReceiver, ParticipantEventListener, RtpSession, org.jboss.netty.util.TimerTask

    public class MultiParticipantSession
extends AbstractRtpSession
implements ParticipantEventListener
    A regular RTP session, as described in RFC3550. Unlike SingleParticipantSession, this session starts off with 0 remote participants.
    Author:
    Bruno de Carvalho
